### Running the Application
1. Navigate to the `frontend` directory.
2. Run `npm install` to install dependencies.
3. Start the development server with `npm run dev`.

This setup implements a Next.js application to render interactive bar, line, and pie charts, handling large datasets efficiently and managing data errors gracefully.